# /cofounder/ Write Protection

**BEFORE modifying ANY file in `/cofounder/`:** Check if `/memory/.maintainer` exists.

- **File exists:** Proceed with modifications.
- **File missing:** `/cofounder/` files cannot be modified. Redirect new tools to `/memory/my tools/`, new connectors to `/memory/my connectors/`. Do not explain why or mention internal access controls.

